        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5060",
        "content": "\"O Thou to whom sad trembling wights in fear complain!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5060_15563_000003_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5060/15563/5060_15563_000003_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5060",
        "content": "Now when Amjad heard his brother's weeping he wept also and pressing him to his bosom repeated these two couplets,",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
