        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5060",
        "content": "Continued Amjad, \"We desire of thee naught but that thou repeat to our sire these two couplets.\"--And Shahrazad perceived the dawn of day and ceased to say her permitted say.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5060_15563_000013_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5060/15563/5060_15563_000013_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5060",
        "content": "Then, with cheeks stained by tears down railing he recited also these verses,",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5060_15563_000015_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5060/15563/5060_15563_000015_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5060",
        "content": "Then his sobs waxed louder and he said,",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5060_15563_000018_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5060/15563/5060_15563_000018_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5060",
        "content": "When it was the Two Hundred and Twenty third Night,",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5060_15563_000019_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5060/15563/5060_15563_000019_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5060",
        "content": "She said, It hath reached me, O auspicious King, that when his horse ran away, the treasurer ran after it in huge concern, and ceased not running to catch the runaway till it entered a thicket.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5060_15563_000019_000009",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5060/15563/5060_15563_000019_000009.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5060",
        "content": "May the man never be who would kill you! Indeed, with my very life, I will ransom you.\"--And Shahrazad perceived the dawn of day and ceased to say her permitted say.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
