        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5060/15563/5060_15563_000020_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5060",
        "content": "When it was the Two Hundred and Twenty fourth Night,",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5060_15563_000021_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5060/15563/5060_15563_000021_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5060",
        "content": "But as for you two, fare ye forth into the lands, for Allah's earth is wide; and know, O my lords, that it paineth me to part from you.\" At this, they all fell a weeping; then the two youths put off their clothes and the treasurer habited them with his own.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-5060_15563_000021_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/5060/15563/5060_15563_000021_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-5060",
        "content": "Moreover he made two parcels of their dress and, filling two vials with the lion's blood, set the parcels before him on his horse's back. Presently he took leave of them and, making his way to the city, ceased not faring till he went in to King Kamar al Zaman and kissed the ground between his hands.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
